Usage: reset_glitch_derate [-help] [-derate_height] [-derate_width]
                           [-glitch_type <string>] [-instance_pin <string>]
                           [-offset] [-pin <string>] [-view <string>]

-help                     # Prints out the command usage
-derate_height            # reset derate height (bool, optional)
-derate_width             # reset derate width (bool, optional)
-glitch_type <string>     # glitch type vl, vh or both (string, optional)
-instance_pin <string>    # instane pin names on which derate is to be reset
                          # (string, optional)
-offset                   # reset derate offset (bool, optional)
-pin <string>             # library pin names on which derate is to be reset
                          # (string, optional)
-view <string>            # view name (string, optional)